+    "offsets_x":[-1.5,-3.0,-4.5],"offsets_y":[0.0,0.0,0.0],"reason":"line after staging"}
+ ]}}
+
+Operator escalation example — the snapshot is empty or marked mcp_stale
+and the error is ambiguous:
